title: The No Jumper Show Ep. 14
description:
Weekly No Jumper Show with Adam22, Cam G1rl and Housephone. This week, Adam22 returns from his New York City trip with stories from Rolling Loud. We got early access to the Lil Peep documentary. BTS members to serve in Korean military. The world is still waiting on new Playboi Carti.
